# Theme Management

The application provides theme customization for pet profiles.

## Theme Components
- [src/models/Theme.js](mdc:src/models/Theme.js) - Theme data model
- [src/models/UserTheme.js](mdc:src/models/UserTheme.js) - User-theme association
- [src/controllers/themeController.js](mdc:src/controllers/themeController.js) - Theme operations
- [src/routes/store.js](mdc:src/routes/store.js) - Theme store endpoints

## Theme Management Flow
1. Admins create and manage themes
2. Users browse available themes in the store
3. Users select themes for their pets
4. Themes are applied to pet profiles

